rvl - reveal
============
A program that reveals info about entries in the Linux's file system. It is
designed to work better with scripting languages.

Requirements
------------
In order to build it, you will only need a C compiler.

Installation
------------
- Compile the rvl.c file.

    cc rvl.c -O3 -o rvl

- Add the binary rvl to your system's PATH variable.

Help
----
Read its help instructions.

    rvl -h
